To plot indicator values, in the OnData event handler, call the Plot method.

private Sum _sum;

// In Initialize()
var symbol = AddEquity("SPY").Symbol;
_sum = SUM(symbol, period);

// In OnData()
if (_sum.IsReady)
{
    Plot("My Indicators", "sum", _sum.Current.Value);
}
